about.summary: C library functions and command line utilities for working with curvilinear grids.

name: gridutils
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.0" %}

package:
    name: gridutils
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/sakov/gridutils-c/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 358e93d2e3431d9e2d4c0574d25d97dd26585204e1e8407e817429f40ebf406e

build:
    number: 1
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - nn
        - csa
    run:
        - nn
        - csa

test:
    commands:
        - gridbathy -h
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test csa  # [not win]

about:
    home: https://github.com/sakov/gridutils-c
    license: BSD 2-Clause
    summary: 'C library functions and command line utilities for working with curvilinear grids.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
